<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每次到地上世界，小美人鱼都觉得不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王子的世界比我的要大得多。”小美人鱼自言自语，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类能在陆地上走，能航海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的生活特别有意思，我的生活太无聊了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼觉得自己更想生活在地上世界，而不是海底王国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天又一天，她一个人坐在自己的花园里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>姐姐们很担心，于是她们去找奶奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奶奶。”大姐说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请跟小美人鱼谈谈，弄清楚她为什么那么忧伤。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，智慧人鱼去看她的孙女，把她抱在怀里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宝贝，告诉我你为什么忧伤。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奶奶。”小美人鱼说，“有永生不死的人吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉过你。”智慧人鱼回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类比我们死得早，但是他们的灵魂会永生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也想拥有灵魂。我想在地上世界生活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的家在这里。”智慧人鱼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“相信我，世界上没有地方比得上海底王国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们在这里都很幸福。这里是我们的家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我想拥有和我的王子一样的灵魂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那样我们俩就能永远在一起了。”小美人鱼坚持说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不需要灵魂。”智慧人鱼坚定说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“作为一个人鱼，你会活很长时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当你死的时候，你会变成美丽的大海泡沫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样，你就能一直是大海的一部分和我们的一部分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼恳求说：“求您了，奶奶，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>告诉我怎么才能得到灵魂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>智慧人鱼意识到她无法改变她孙女的想法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我听说人鱼一定要和一个人类结婚。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186277</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的王子必须要爱上你，并且和你结婚，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你才能变成拥有灵魂的人类。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，我要做的就是和王子结婚？”小美人鱼充满希望地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不确定。”智慧人鱼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉你的只是一个古老的传说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我没听说过有人鱼得到灵魂或想拥有灵魂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们没有灵魂，也生活得很幸福。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，小美人鱼听不进去奶奶的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经在忙着思考和制定计划了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奶奶，为了在地上世界生活，我必须做什么？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要再想了。”智慧人鱼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要想生活在那里，你得有腿和脚。”她摸了摸孙女的头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为你有美丽的尾巴，你不可能在陆地上生活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼不开心地看着自己的尾巴，叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我讨厌我的尾巴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>智慧人鱼摇头说：“你很漂亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在去玩儿吧。别想地上世界了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼游走了，但是她没玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想：“一定有办法的。一定有人能帮我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许海巫婆能帮助我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>